'''Eport''' was [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy's]] largest auction house, found in the wondrous [[City/Legends|city]] of [[Bidamount]], where beings from across the galaxy could bid on obscure and often suddenly valuable merchandise. Eport claimed a large percentage of the final price as well as the opening bid, and many believed that additional funding came from secret and sinister sources.

[[Sholh Dorr]] sold [[3B6-RA-7]] at Eport for over a thousand times what he had originally paid.

